sourcesContent: function _hash(r){var t,n=0;if(0===r.length)return n;for(t=0;t<r.length;t++)n=(n<<5)-n+r.charCodeAt(t),n|=0;return n}function hashRandom(){return _hash((new Date).getTime()+"_"+Math.random())}function hashString(r){return _hash(r)}function hashObject(r){return _hash("object"==typeof r?JSON.stringify(r):"")}function hashArray(r){return _hash("object"==typeof r&&Array.isArray(r)?JSON.stringify(r):"")}module.exports={ hashRandom, hashString, hashObject, hashArray }
